{"tid":2231511,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[童年回憶系列] 一人多個而家香港冇左嘅地方","createTime":"2020-10-05T16:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T15:04:11.000Z","uid":218209,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ae411c22e072cabd879881614788a7d05ed67da6","tid":2231511,"uid":218209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:52:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>又一城熱帶雨林餐廳</strong><br />\n又驚又想去食 未食到已經執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rbap5aN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbap5aN.jpg&h=4974aa2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Re9BWht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRe9BWht.jpg&h=13ca5ff9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70yGnXt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70yGnXt.jpg&h=f4f2484d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>青衣城</strong><br />\n好掛住個潛水員 同掛喺中庭嘅海盜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RBTCFKJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRBTCFKJ.jpg&h=49e3b58d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2USDqbp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2USDqbp.jpg&h=e1998426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>青衣城舊墟</strong><br />\n好似去咗舊時香港咁 <br />\n記得好鍾意喺嗰度整手蠟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjQNiw9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjQNiw9.jpg&h=3a2a0b9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w0bMy5v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw0bMy5v.jpg&h=001555d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>山頂 信不信由你博物館</strong><br />\n去完一次發左成個月惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家大個左好想去番<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gf8fsqU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgf8fsqU.jpg&h=5f9c9c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fNH0DxA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfNH0DxA.jpg&h=41d2632a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPxgbSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPxgbSB.jpg&h=51403e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>愉景新城Disney Store<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n未有迪士尼就係呢度買迪士尼野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgv5PEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqgv5PEA.jpg&h=0b32fbd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>尖沙咀小熊國</strong><br />\n有去過但冇咩深刻印象<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/65wdd6s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F65wdd6s.jpg&h=0bdbe306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>朗豪坊星座展品</strong><br />\n每層都有 而家冇哂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mKbTYyu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmKbTYyu.jpg&h=c5627e6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b369d7563c88a1c6f41dd430290590e0bb3a94ae","tid":2231511,"uid":57073,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"沙田噴水池<br />\n皇室堡刀手燈柱"},{"pid":"58a6a0136ed90ea0ac831b81863054349e9d57ca","tid":2231511,"uid":80503,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:55:47.000Z","msg":"超人餐廳<br />\n同埋真正既香港"},{"pid":"0a07df2949036827b57e9f3c052f2574d0e69e66","tid":2231511,"uid":238883,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RBTCFKJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRBTCFKJ.jpg&h=49e3b58d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我記得呢個位, 再以前係 Starbucks <br />\n平時係D咖啡機買開 cappuccino , 個日走左去starbucks買一杯<br />\n太重奶味, 行返轉頭同佢講, 可唔可以幫我加返D朱古力粉落去<br />\n飲唔到太重奶味<br />\n點知佢好好人, 直接幫我換左做mocha<br />\n個時應該係2001年12月 _ 日"},{"pid":"da2fd5994e85a1d760811b6fad49b7b3646bbf0